text: The Nguyễn Dynasty was the last imperial dynasty, or family of rulers, in Vietnamese history. ==History== The Nguyễn emperors ruled from 1802 to 1945. The capital of the Nguyễn dynasty was Huế. Nearly 40 percent of all Vietnamese people have the family name Nguyễn, named after the dynasty. ===Princes=== ===Emperors=== ==References== Category:1802 establishments Category:1945 disestablishments Category:Colonialism Category:Former countries in Southeast Asia Category:Former empires Category:Former monarchies of Asia Category:History of Vietnam Category:Noble families Category:People from Huế
